flowchart LR
    subgraph Edge[Edge Zone]
        GW[API Gateway]
        SIGN[Header Signature Service]
    end

    subgraph Mesh[Service Mesh Zone]
        MTLS[mTLS / Workload Identity]
        B1[Backend Service]
        AUTHZ[In-service Authorization Check]
    end

    subgraph Policy[Control Plane]
        OPA[Policy Engine]
    end

    C[Client] --> GW
    GW --> SIGN
    SIGN --> B1
    MTLS --> B1
    B1 --> AUTHZ
    AUTHZ --> OPA

    NOTE1[Only trusted caller identity accepted]
    NOTE2[Signed context + freshness validation]

    B1 -.-> NOTE1
    SIGN -.-> NOTE2
